<li><strong><a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/standard-tap">standard-tap</a></strong> - Format JavaScript Standard Style as TAP output</li>
<li><strong><a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/standard-json">standard-json</a></strong> - Format JavaScript Standard Style output to a JSON array</li>
<li><strong><a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/standard-reporter">standard-reporter</a></strong> - Reporters for feross/standard via unix pipes, many options</li>
<h2>build tools</h2>
