<li><strong><a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/gulp-standard">gulp-standard</a></strong> - Gulp plugin for standard</li>
<li><strong><a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/mocha-standard">mocha-standard</a></strong> - Integrates standard into your mocha tests</li>
<li><strong><a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/standard-loader">standard-loader</a></strong> - Lint webpack builds with standard</li>
